																				<h1 class="page-title">Careers</h1>										
															<div class="spacer10 hidden-xs"></div>					
					<div class="hidden-xs title-hr"></div>					
										
										
					
					
<div class="text-style">
	<p>In order to continue to support the company strategy and meet the demands of the industry, ISP is currently recruiting top quality talent in a variety of roles to join our team.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Careers within ISP are varied and dynamic, offering the opportunity to explore a variety of operational divisions.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Deep scientific knowledge and unparalleled understanding within the production and exploration domains are critical, together with excellent interpersonal skills and a spark of passion and inspiration that sets you apart from the rest of the crowd. If you embrace new technologies and are proactive in seeking out new skills and techniques to continually improve product offerings, we would love to hear from you.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>We have typically recruited candidates with the following backgrounds/experience:</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>Degree in geosciences/maths related disciplines (masters degree beneficial but not essential)</li>
<li>Oil and gas upstream domain experience</li>
<li>High level of understanding and knowledge of upstream domain tools and software</li>
<li>High level of understanding of modern upstream domain workflows</li>
<li>C++ development expertise</li>
<li>Knowledge / understanding / expertise of using C#, Javascript, PHP, python&#8230;</li>
<li>Previous experience working within an operator / service company / software consultancy</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>To apply or request more information, please contact <strong><a href="mailto:info@ispforum.com">info@ispforum.com</a></strong>.</p>
</div>

